events.location: Fort Worth, Texas, United States Of America
events.description: Doors open one hour prior to showtime. Venue box office opens one hour prior to door time. Closing hours vary per event. All sales are subject to increase the day of the show. Support acts are subject to change without notice. Bag Policy: Bags up to 12"x6"x12" are allowed in the venue. All bags will be searched prior to entry. Mobile Tickets: Your phone is your ticket! Download your tickets into your mobile wallet and transfer to friends via www.livenation.com or the Live Nation app. Ticket Help: https://help.livenation.com/ Parking: Ride-share service is encouraged. Valet parking is available near the entrance to Tannahill's on Exchange Street for $20. Paid lots within short walking distance. Venue FAQ page: https://www.tannahills.com/connect/faqs Dining by Chef Tim Love: https://www.tannahills.com/food-drink VIP seating: vip@tannahills.com/AVAILABILITY
